1. *Rekao* sam mu da dođe ovde. (I told him to come here.)
2. Kako *reći* "volim te" na francuskom jeziku? (How to say "I love you" in French?)
3. Ona *kaže* da je spremna za intervju. (She says she's ready for the interview.)
4. Nikad ne znam šta će on *reći* sledeće. (I never know what he's going to say next.)
5. Hoćeš li *reći* nešto na sastanku? (Will you say something at the meeting?)
6. *Rečeno* mi je da je koncert već rasprodan. (I was told that the concert is already sold out.)
7. Ukoliko nešto nije jasno, slobodno *recite*. (If something is not clear, feel free to say.)
8. Kada ne možete da *nađete reči*, pokažite gestovima. (When you can't find the words, use gestures.)
9. Ona me je *prekorela* što nisam ništa *rekao*. (She scolded me for not saying anything.)
10. Šta bi ti *rekao* da ti kažem da moramo odložiti putovanje? (What would you say if I told you we have to postpone the trip?)